# YouTube Short Notes

📝 A Chrome extension for taking timestamped notes on YouTube videos with folder organization.

## Features

- ⏱️ Add notes at specific video timestamps
- 📂 Organize notes into folders
- 🔍 Quickly jump back to important moments
- 🎨 Clean Material Design interface

## Installation

### Chrome Web Store
1. [Install from Chrome Web Store](#) *(Link when published)*

### Manual Installation
1. Download this repository
2. Open Chrome and go to `chrome://extensions`
3. Enable "Developer mode" (toggle top-right)
4. Click "Load unpacked" and select the extension folder

## How to Use

1. Click the extension icon while watching a YouTube video
2. Use the "+" button to add a note at the current timestamp
3. Create folders to organize your notes
4. Click any note to jump to that moment in the video

